{"tid":193004,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"我叫阿俊 係一條廢柴","createTime":"2017-04-09T04:13:12.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-09T14:14:04.000Z","uid":61876,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"349980146c8407ecd9c654ab8d9f5dc1225b6d8d","tid":193004,"uid":61876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T04:13:12.000Z","msg":"序"},{"pid":"ba88aac7d481bf14c67cea24a4d7419c2ddfe1e0","tid":193004,"uid":61876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T04:13:37.000Z","msg":"頂未打完"},{"pid":"0999bf7e4cf1ed0bd56a60709c423c5b7c62d1a3","tid":193004,"uid":77769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T04:14:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"472d7cb6e695e64e22c7e6fec9a3701d956204cb","tid":193004,"uid":36600,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T04:18:13.000Z","msg":"俊？邊撚到俊？睇過～～"},{"pid":"af764cbaea69c7b7ecd3de71ffff3e6619bec1f2","tid":193004,"uid":61876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T04:42:53.000Z","msg":"序<br />\n「叮噹叮噹」返學嘅鐘聲響起<br />\n隨著微風吹過，我嘅暑假同埋稚嫩都係呢一陣風中吹走左。 校門前嘅大樹微微招搖，好似係到歡迎緊我咁。「希望今年可以大步檻過。」我心中默念。<br />\n唔記得自我介紹，我叫阿俊，今年中四，4c啊<br />\n我知你想講咩，得啦我一啲都唔靚仔，仲有少少面目可憎添，而且只係得米七，係一個得閒打下波，打下機嘅廢青so9sad<br />\n今年嘅我好好彩都係我班老死一班，睇嚟今年都係不得安寧嫁啦。<br />\n今日一番到課室就feel到一股好強嘅殺氣，我托一托眼鏡望過去，「嘟嘟嘟嘟 boom」戰鬥力竟然有9999，原來個位係人稱西面方丈嘅 miss箘。<br />\n正當我諗住今年有排捱嘅時候，有一把聲傳過嚟:「請大家支持籃社一號候選內閣 breakers」<br />\n佢把聲真係好won耳，正當我諗緊邊個嘈鳩住二十八座大王思考嘅時候，我見到一個好似木偶嘅女仔<br />\n而我不自量力嘅故事就係由呢到開始。"},{"pid":"d014956f47b10c44cbe2d72c5217877278e5f1b6","tid":193004,"uid":61876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T04:43:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>俊？邊撚到俊？睇過～～</blockquote><br />\n估撚到"},{"pid":"dd24bf14af4d031270cedbe729073386addcbdb2","tid":193004,"uid":61876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T04:43:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n有貨了"},{"pid":"4cd9839ae4d319cbf8d2afee233bbcf3aa0f2b9f","tid":193004,"uid":61876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T05:10:16.000Z","msg":"第一章 社選舉<br />\n<br />\n開學已經有個幾月，而我亦都聽左d人嗌on9口號嗌個幾月。每次個位擁有環迴立體聲嘅木偶嚟宣傳，我都會望實佢，望到佢收皮為止。我d老死個鳩個以為我鍾意佢，叫我放棄，話人地係社長，而且已經中五，我高攀唔起。我即刻屌撚到佢地啪啪聲，成地都係精<br />\n終於於去到社選舉嘅日子。<br />\n個日嘅下晝簡直係嘈撚到拆天，身為東華三院嘅一分子，我覺得學校應該拉曬班社幹事去歡樂滿東華撐埸，拋一抛隔離班小保良都好啊嘛。<br />\n好好彩，我就係紅社嘅，唔洗聽木偶妹鳩叫，如果唔係我都驚我沖上去玩菜刀無雙，全場八死十七傷。點解八死？因為一個內閣有八個人lor,其中有一個仲係我老死，佢叫阿杰，真係鄧佢隻耳仔辛苦。<br />\n選舉結果顯然易見，全部順利當選，因為每個社都只係得一個內閣去選。除左紅同藍社之外仲有紫同黃四個社。<br />\n屌你老母八四三十二個人係操場比小鳳姐集體上身鳩叫慶祝，一個字 好撚嘈。<br />\n我頭也不回地沖左出學校，唔知點解好似係巴士站都聽到木偶妹鳩叫咁"},{"pid":"8012178a7a7cd2be2ae5ed95454d68eb449bf746","tid":193004,"uid":61876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T05:11:02.000Z","msg":"今晚繼續 ，睇反應 <br />\nBtw誰偷偷留下負皮"},{"pid":"73d0deceaf1b6836b679a2fe51400258c06f506b","tid":193004,"uid":7411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T05:13:17.000Z","msg":"負評潮撐<br />\n<br />\n利申：睇左個序字"},{"pid":"bdd6a3aafae5c7e963e48bdc2438853378952242","tid":193004,"uid":61876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T05:15:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>負評潮撐<br />\n<br />\n利申：睇左個序字</blockquote><br />\n大佬比次機會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2f81eacafe695d844b4500a77de0ba41a3dd15b","tid":193004,"uid":61876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T05:20:40.000Z","msg":"自知文筆差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但只係想分享下自己個故事"},{"pid":"94f350a1d9bac46c553c72902dc05f76b129caa5","tid":193004,"uid":7411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T07:37:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自知文筆差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但只係想分享下自己個故事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試下唔好用口語啦<br />\n加太多野<br />\n睇落麻麻"},{"pid":"b8ebf68235c55ece02883047af9b26e2ec941694","tid":193004,"uid":83440,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T10:34:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c60873a8c390309cf6d4f0b33aaef2217a1ae37c","tid":193004,"uid":61876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:13:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>自知文筆差<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但只係想分享下自己個故事</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n試下唔好用口語啦<br />\n加太多野<br />\n睇落麻麻</blockquote><br />\n我怕用書面語會太formal<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以全口語 btw thx"},{"pid":"30ba593c6756973cacddd8a153c8f1572af0a9ce","tid":193004,"uid":61876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T14:14:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你個名<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}